Queen Sarah Benz is the current Queen of Aso Culture and was recently crowned at the grandeur event held at popular Grand Cubana Hotel, Jabi, Abuja. The event which featured some notable personalities within and outside Abuja was a massive success. After her engagements in series of camp and stage activities, she emerged victorious as the new Queen of Aso Culture. Previously, Queen Sarah has contested in a few pageant show and emerged Queen Of Benue Tourism Nigeria and recently crowned Queen Of Aso Culture, 2020/2021. The multi-talented Sarah Benz also doubles as a philanthropist and a skin therapist. The CEO of Sarah Benz Empire promised to make a change during her tenure as the queen of aso culture through her pet project and other activities, in addition to her records of several awards. She has previously bagged Outstanding Queen of the Year 2017, Indigenous North Central Queen of the Year, and a certified organic cream producer and more. She has promised to use her new title to touch the lives of the downtrodden in the society.